entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: I spoke with Loisya Starkos and they helped me get a new Elder Robe.  I should go visit her again if I want to replace it in the future.
entries.journal_entry_description: I need to speak with Loisya Starkos
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: I need to travel to The Temple of Exar Kun on Yavin 4.  The Ancient Relic should be somewhere in the area.
entries.task01_journal_entry_title: Retrieve the Ancient Relic from Yavin 4
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: I need to travel to the Krayt Graveyard on Tatooine.  The Ancient Relic should be somewhere in the area.
entries.task02_journal_entry_title: Retrieve the Ancient Relic from Tatooine
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: I need to travel to the site of the Corsec vs. Flail Battle on Talus.  The Ancient Relic should be somewhere in the area.
entries.task03_journal_entry_title: Retrieve the Ancient Relic from Talus
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: I need to travel to the Great Kimogila Skeleton on Lok.  The Ancient Relic should be somewhere in the area.
entries.task04_journal_entry_title: Retrieve the Ancient Relic from Lok
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: I need to travel to the Dulok Village on Endor.  The Ancient Relic should be somewhere in the area.
entries.task05_journal_entry_title: Retrieve the Ancient Relic from Endor
entries.task06_journal_entry_description: I need to travel to the Jedi Temple Ruins on Dantooine.  The Ancient Relic should be somewhere in the area.
entries.task06_journal_entry_title: Retrieve the Ancient Relic from Dantooine
entries.task07_journal_entry_description: I need to gather the Ancient Relics from Dantooine, Endor, Lok, Talus, Tatooine, and Yavin 4.
entries.task08_journal_entry_description: In order to receive a new Elder Robe give it to Loisya Starkos.
entries.task08_journal_entry_title: Give your Elder Robe to Loisya Starkos
entries.task09_journal_entry_description: Speak to Loisya Starkos again to receive your new robe.
